<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<!-- @import "components/head.html" -->

<body tabIndex="0">
  <!-- @import "components/header.html" -->
  <main>
    <section class="category">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title category__title">Shop</h1>
        <nav class="category__nav" aria-label="breadcrumb">
          <ol class="nav">
            <li class="nav__item">
              <a href="#acne-care" class="nav__link nav__link--active" aria-current="page">Acne care</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav__item">
              <a href="#hair-care" class="nav__link" role="menuitem">Hair care</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav__item">
              <a href="#skin-care" class="nav__link" role="menuitem">Skin care</a>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <ul class="category__products" role="none">
          <li class="product-item category__product">
            <div class="product-item__image">
              <img src="img/product-sample.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="product-item__info">
              <h2 class="product-item__title">Acne starter kit</h2>
              <p class="product-item__price">$ 60.00</p>
              <a href="product-page.html" class="btn btn--black">Go to product</a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="product-item category__product">
            <div class="product-item__image">
              <img src="img/product-sample.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="product-item__info">
              <h2 class="product-item__title">Acne starter kit</h2>
              <p class="product-item__price">$ 60.00</p>
              <a href="product-page.html" class="btn btn--black">Go to product</a>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="benefits">
      <div class="container">
        <ul class="benefits__cards" role="none">
          <li class="benefits__card">
            <div class="benefits__content">
              <div class="benefits__info">
                <h2 class="benefits__title">Charity Work</h2>
                <p class="benefits__text">
                  Our work aligns with the work of many charitable organisations and foundations that are focused on
                  creating a brighter
                  future for all. Our plan sees us expanding our social initiatives and building on our charitable work
                  to
                  enable us to
                  offer up our help to a bigger audience, to those most in need of our support.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefits__image">
              <picture>
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/charity-lg-2x.webp 2x" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/charity-lg-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/charity-lg-1x.jpg" class="background" alt="a tree's branch on a beige background"
                  srcset="img/benefits/charity-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
              <picture>
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-overlay-sm-1x.webp, img/benefits/charity-overlay-sm-2x.webp 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-overlay-sm-1x.jpg, img/benefits/charity-overlay-sm-2x.jpg 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-2x.webp 2x"
                  type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x"
                  type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-1x.jpg" class="positioned" alt="a woman's face with freckles"
                  srcset="img/benefits/charity-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefits__card benefits__card--reversed">
            <div class="benefits__content">
              <div class="benefits__info">
                <h2 class="benefits__title">Our Ingredients</h2>
                <p class="benefits__text">
                  Safisa is committed to using only natural ingredients in our products. Why? Because it’s intuitive, it
                  makes sense to
                  us. Human skin responds best to ingredients that it encounters in a natural setting and so we aim to
                  mimic this with our
                  cosmetics. Therefore you will find that our products can be used on sensitive skin and the risks of
                  any adverse reaction
                  are an absolute rarity. Our products are made with a universal audience in mind after all.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefits__image benefits__image--reversed">
              <picture>
                <source srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/ingredients-lg-2x.webp 2x"
                  type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/ingredients-lg-2x.jpg 2x"
                  type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/ingredients-lg-1x.jpg" class="background" alt="ocean with white foam"
                  srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
              <picture>
                <source
                  srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-sm-1x.webp, img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-sm-2x.webp 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp">
                <source
                  srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-sm-1x.jpg, img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-sm-2x.jpg 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg">
                <source
                  srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-2x.webp 2x"
                  type="image/webp">
                <source
                  srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x"
                  type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-1x.jpg" class="positioned positioned--reversed"
                  alt="a woman's tanned face" srcset="img/benefits/ingredients-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="benefits__card">
            <div class="benefits__content">
              <div class="benefits__info">
                <h2 class="benefits__title">Animal Testing</h2>
                <p class="benefits__text">
                  We find the cruel process of testing cosmetics on animals to be abhorrent and we stand firm in our
                  belief that the
                  pursuit of beauty cannot be found in nature’s suffering. All of our products are made with ingredients
                  that have not
                  been needlessly tested on animals and, instead, we have used progressive laboratory methods of testing
                  including “in
                  vitro” processes that avoid the need to harm living creatures.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefits__image">
              <picture>
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/testing-lg-2x.webp 2x" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/testing-lg-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/testing-lg-1x.jpg" class="background"
                  alt="some green leaves on the light background" srcset="img/benefits/testing-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
              <picture>
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-overlay-sm-1x.webp, img/benefits/testing-overlay-sm-2x.webp 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-overlay-sm-1x.jpg, img/benefits/testing-overlay-sm-2x.jpg 2x"
                  media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-1x.webp, img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-2x.webp 2x"
                  type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-1x.jpg, img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x"
                  type="image/jpeg">
                <img src="img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-1x.jpg" class="positioned"
                  alt="a woman with a fluffy cat in her arms" srcset="img/benefits/testing-overlay-lg-2x.jpg 2x">
              </picture>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <!-- @import "components/footer.html" -->
  <!-- @import "components/scripts.html" -->
</body>

</html>